title: BIP 48: Treasury USDC Productivity
body:
TLDR; Earn a basket of promising, upcoming, or saleable assets by using idle treasury assets; increase diversification, acquire utilities, further the decentralized stable asset market.

Results
1) Expense multiplier: Base Case - 2X multiplier on 18 months of retained runway
2) Agreement with risk structure and position of presented assets
3) 60/30/10 split of assets between Tranches A, B, and C
